od for asked  \nfor their family members. Please Help this Student.\n\n8.2. Will you recommend this student for this scholarship?\n\n\u2612 Yes \u2610 No \u2610 Not Sure\n\n8.3. Any other comments you want to share?\n\nShe has a twin and one elder sister; Three women's  \nis build career at different ways; Her parents struggling to grow /  \nmove to help with their studies.\n\nVolunteer Signature\n\nM.S. \u2014\u2014\u2014\u2014\n\nCo-Volunteer Signature\n\nNisanthar. J",
